50">Wien</placeName><date when="1910-11-25" n="01">25. 11. 1910</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName><date when="1910-11-25">25. 11. 1910</date></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11036">Burckhard, Max</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1910-04-23_01">Burckhard an Schnitzler, 23. 4. 1910</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1911-08-23_01">Burckhard an Schnitzler, 23. 8. 1911</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
